{"tid":1248850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HK01:警評估影響比佔中大","createTime":"2019-06-21T14:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T14:55:35.000Z","uid":41404,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"63afdb44c5918acd4bf83f69b286876ea1430ba7","tid":1248850,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"警方消息透露，今日下午有二、三千人加入示威行動，對公共及緊急服務構成影響，影響程度比2014年佔中為大，其中999的服務受阻，一旦發生嚴重事件或刑事案件時，未必可能即時派員處理。消息指，警方暫無計劃清場，會觀察放工後的示威人數增長及民情變化。若示威人數增加至二萬人以上時，示威者抗爭或會維持一段時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/343401/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F343401%2F&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=aaceb3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/343401/</a>"},{"pid":"534722acedb3fc92c205c93352ffaf1d696dc1ae","tid":1248850,"uid":73381,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"毅進制二萬=幾十萬架啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c536ebdc6adee5350fd5d47a8aa54ebf6d5cf6a2","tid":1248850,"uid":10757,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56196a139c5b2d5a0968025ec1624f45bb461106","tid":1248850,"uid":11301,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:38:21.000Z","msg":"又有無大肚婆去唔到律敦治呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f99d9c4902e27af5b312c240375a2c85475a19","tid":1248850,"uid":1789,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:38:33.000Z","msg":"一早放四千警力落狗屋<br />\n但賴阻住999服務？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0747c91c427c3f779f20589dbead2f43a301e657","tid":1248850,"uid